
START

Output: "Welcome to Benjamins's store"
Output: "Please enter the current Tarriff percentage"
   Input tariff1

If tariff1 is not a number
   Output: "Please enter a valid Tarriff percentage, (hint: its a number)"
   Input tariff1

Set principal to 10.00
Set quantity to 10
Set delivery to 6.99
Set years to 2.0
Set timesPerYear to 4

Create investment item with above values and tariff1

Call attr() to display item metadata
Call info() to display item details

Output: "Congrats on your credit card approval, please enter intrest rate"
   Input rate1

If rate1 is not a number
   Output: "Please enter a valid number, I cannot read your intent"
   Input rate1

Set item rate to rate1
Calculate compound interest
Call compound() to display cost after interest

Clone scanner
Output: "Please enter updated Tarriff percentage"
   Input tariff2

Set item tariff to tariff2
Call attr() to display item metadata
Call info() to display item details

Output: "Please enter updated intrest rate"
   Input rate2

Set item rate to rate2
Calculate compound interest
Call compound() to display updated cost

Close scanner

END
